## Conventions

- Entities in separate files by domain
- Snake_case with `name:` for database columns
- `@Index` on foreign keys for performance
- `create` + `save` (never direct `insert` for hooks to work)
- QueryBuilder for complex queries, Repository for simple CRUD
- Migrations named with timestamp
